

Project- Basic python calculator.
A simple Python-based calculator that performs basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. 
This program is user-friendly, handles invalid inputs gracefully, and allows multiple calculations in a single session.


How to use this calculator.


step 1 :- choose  1 2 3 4 as respectively according to lebeling of the addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

step 2 :- Enter the digits and calculate the output.

step 3 :- get your answer.
